Located 40 to 50 meters away from the resort city of [[Le Yer]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]], '''Phyrstal Island''' was a small part of land known for its population comprised mostly of eccentric artists and entertainers. It had approximately 3000 residents. It was home to numerous establishments such as the [[Lost Loves Casino]], the [[Starlight Theater]], and [[Njinska's Tavern]]. It was once a popular resort/amusement park area, but fell on hard times and ended up as run-down and seedy.

The waters near Phyrstal island were known to be home to pirates which would raid stray ships or yachts. Visitors could use a [[hydrobike]] to get to the island, and there was also a ferry that left every morning from Le Yer which was considered safer. Once there, one could visit one of the numerous pawn shops, gift shops, and restaurants.

